comments.body: About this sphere v2.1 I followed this project from the beginning and was earning from the rebase which was 1.9% every 24hrs and the rebase happens every 30 minutes a day. Before the migrated to new contract and moved all liquidity to Tatu dex swap. Now they have come up with new idea of making the token deflationary token. I really don't think swapping and moving to new contract is really a good thing for every project and even if any of this is to happen they should have added all this on their roadmap and do it at ones.. Now the token price is very down from it's all time high and their is no sign of getting back high again .
